</style><h3 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading">WACTOR 生产相关文章</h3><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="V2oM9cMNU5"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/wactor-production-should-face-the-voices-of-latin-american-listeners-and-fans-in-response-to-the-successive-suspensions-of-affiliated-vtuber/">针对附属VTuber活动的接连停止，WACTOR Productions应该面对的拉丁美洲观众和粉丝的声音</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“针对附属 VTuber 的活动连续暂停，WACTOR Productions 应该面对拉丁美洲观众和粉丝的声音” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/wactor-production-should-face-the-voices-of-latin-american-listeners-and-fans-in-response-to-the-successive-suspensions-of-affiliated-vtuber/embed/#?secret=zixz8TMVfc#?secret=V2oM9cMNU5" data-secret="V2oM9cMNU5" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="VtbWY9p6tQ"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-agency-wactor-production-hina-misora-suspension-without-notice-triggers-concern-about-the-current-state/">VTuber办公室WACTOR Production Voices对日南空“中断”造成的现状表示担忧</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber办公室WACTOR制作之声对日南空“中断”后的现状表示担忧” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-agency-wactor-production-hina-misora-suspension-without-notice-triggers-concern-about-the-current-state/embed/#?secret=uEIm5JVVmu#?secret=VtbWY9p6tQ" data-secret="VtbWY9p6tQ" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote 